/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n服牛屎一督，牛屎性溫味苦，其臭無毒，遇痔外服半督內服半督，即三日內可癒。"},{"pid":"64fb90fdb9ef2936782b5c0eddb1b20d28624879","tid":337292,"uid":83852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:43:40.000Z","msg":"單思"},{"pid":"9fdf661b800c0356574721ff689fd4a8ededbb3e","tid":337292,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:43:46.000Z","msg":"大肚腩"},{"pid":"fa4f02d210d8d6e69eff94b1c6a01287a87dbfaa","tid":337292,"uid":50131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"鼻敏感<br />\n長期有痰咳唔出 做帶氧運動好易會覺嘔心<br />\n求解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58901d0dd90bd5fbd7de84b23dc96a3d5404164","tid":337292,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:45:15.000Z","msg":"成日硬膠開垃圾post ，冇人笑得自己笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8c63ce1d0c421d352e15f7c57cab33ac80a46a6","tid":337292,"uid":117784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:45:50.000Z","msg":"鼻敏感"},{"pid":"33d7f32d6c741670522b10d65d2a5d1d49fcf679","tid":337292,"uid":29241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:46:16.000Z","msg":"失眠<br />\n喉嚨痕"},{"pid":"859bc380bd12e82f0ea3cff9c06820a5a06cfaac","tid":337292,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:46:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>癌</blockquote><br />\n可服瑪啡，瑪啡性烈而味苦，藥性迅猛，可寧神止痛，長期即癌不退亦可息命止痛。"},{"pid":"36ef26b7289cea5864f1943b9bba5b95715f4546","tid":337292,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:48:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>失眠<br />\n喉嚨痕</blockquote><br />\n可服龍角之散，龍角為神龍之角磨粉而成，性涼而味甘，入喉即止炎症，服藥直乾不宜濕，一日三服，三日入即癒"},{"pid":"4bd752ef8a0df482f3790a648aecef116f0b4c0c","tid":337292,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:50:04.000Z","msg":"濕熱 啲屎痴住馬桶沖唔走"},{"pid":"533d42c102512bae952c85e8f4367373bac41ae1","tid":337292,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>單思</blockquote><br />\n可服牛肚一個，牛肚性溫味咸，能載單思之苦，以五香粉烹煮，其味更住，服後即可解其單思"},{"pid":"d745a4b9db9748dc19810d189d19b60c432d4c2a","tid":337292,"uid":15831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:52:15.000Z","msg":"濕疹"},{"pid":"0717e3bdedf740d7f1c457ef54e64c343d632448","tid":337292,"uid":49290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:53:00.000Z","msg":"失眠"},{"pid":"047afa8a1353a8088a8ceee73b559fd031c7a35b","tid":337292,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>濕熱 啲屎痴住馬桶沖唔走</blockquote><br />\n宜啜濕鳩一條，其便不能去為過乾所至，濕鳩性濕而味咸，雖有異臭然可潤便，啜至其出精華而服之，即濕熱可除"},{"pid":"fa101405f7769c9fad94c25e0ebb5c19bcdf1530","tid":337292,"uid":127333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T07:59:59.000Z","msg":"係咁放響屁 但唔臭"},{"pid":"7edad3a8aad62aae0768017fc19411feeb247619","tid":337292,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:00:53.000Z","msg":"暗瘡"}]}